以裁定駁回\r\n上訴。\r\n中　　華　　民　　國　　111 　年　　6 　　月　　30　　日\r\n                          　　書記官  李采錡","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/SJEV/111%2c%e9%87%8d%e5%b0%8f%2c1511%2c20220630%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"SJEV,111,重小,1511,20220630,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"重小","JNO":"1511","JDATE":"20220630","JTITLE":"清償借款"}